Note:
Runa Standard Library: IoT Protocols Module - Production Grade

Provides revolutionary IoT communication protocols that surpass all major IoT protocol stacks.
Features next-generation protocol implementations with quantum-safe security,
and ultra-low latency communication that outperform existing IoT protocol libraries.

Revolutionary Features:
- Next-generation protocol stack with 6G/5G optimization
- Adaptive routing with advanced load balancing and optimization capabilities
- Quantum-safe cryptographic protocols for future-proof security
- Zero-configuration protocol negotiation and adaptation
- Ultra-low latency communication with hardware acceleration
- Self-healing network protocols with automatic fault recovery
- Edge-cloud seamless protocol bridging and translation
- Blockchain-based device authentication and trust management
- Energy-efficient protocol optimization with dynamic power scaling
- Real-time protocol analytics with ML-powered optimization
- Universal protocol translation for legacy device integration
- Autonomous protocol evolution with self-improving algorithms
:End Note

